given a number where even digits should be replaced with their squares and odd digits should be kept the same, reflect the output in the same manner.

public static string transformnumber(String num){
StringBuilder result=new StringBuilder();
for(char ch:num.toCharArray()){
int d= ch-'0';
if(d%2==0){
result.append(d*d);
}else {
result.append(d);
}
}
return result.toString();
}
